</a><br />\n<br />\n全香港所有銀行加埋都無300億現金<br />\n佔整體流通貨幣唔夠6%<br />\n即係9成半現金其實都唔係銀行到（eg. 借左出去尤其中資）<br />\n<br />\n只要60萬人 每人提5萬<br />\n銀行都已經$1都無<br />\n只要大家都提得幾多得幾多<br />\n已經足夠癱瘓銀行既現金流<br />\n嚴重衝擊銀行體系<br />\n簡單直接有力迫使林鄭回應訴求<br />\n比起罷工同流血花算得多！"},{"pid":"b30da0319d1131fbd5911c5688925c8a34261226","tid":1475171,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7tEaWpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7tEaWpt.jpg&h=5b030428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WG2S9Ks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWG2S9Ks.png&h=59abfb8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwvabXN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwvabXN.jpg&h=aa5d2549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqzBRXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqzBRXO.jpg&h=1c3c0e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ11iCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ11iCN.jpg&h=56acb8ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDCjPKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDCjPKt.jpg&h=67a53292&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faf422a8099b1c7c83393fb0d4efedd07ba465e4","tid":1475171,"uid":78046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"我嗰邊3部機2部都冇港紙 <br />\n啱啱去見有個人係咁撳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a219034c2cf0ccdb403b28620cd2bda7f3996508","tid":1475171,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:00:20.000Z","msg":"日日㩒D"}]}